org.interpss.spring
Class NumericSpringFactory

java.lang.Object
  org.interpss.spring.NumericSpringFactory

public class NumericSpringFactory
extends java.lang.Object

for object creation from the Spring container. There are two methods - one for creating object using its default implementation, and the other using user supplied Spring bean id
